ous ordures dans la", "words": [135, 136, 137, 138]}, {"id": 25, "text": "pour regarder la télévision.", "words": [139, 140, 141, 142]}, {"id": 26, "text": "1 2 3 4.", "words": [143, 144, 145, 146]}, {"id": 27, "text": "Élodie réchauffe un plat surgelé dans le four à 5.", "words": [147, 148, 149, 150, 151, 152, 153, 154, 155, 156]}, {"id": 28, "text": "6 7 8 9", "words": [157, 158, 159, 160]}, {"id": 29, "text": "Avant de se coucher, Félix éteint sa lampe de", "words": [161, 162, 163, 164, 165, 166, 167, 168, 169]}, {"id": 30, "text": ".", "words": [170]}, {"id": 31, "text": "Mes vêtements sont suspendus sur des", "words": [171, 172, 173, 174, 175, 176]}, {"id": 32, "text": ".", "words": [177]}, {"id": 33, "text": "le d'eau chaude pour se laver les mains.", "words": [178, 179, 180, 181, 182, 183, 184, 185]}, {"id": 34, "text": ".", "words": [186]}, {"id": 35, "text": "Pour dormir, je pose ma tête sur un", "words": [187, 188, 189, 190, 191, 192, 193, 194]}, {"id": 36, "text": ".", "words": [195]}, {"id": 37, "text": "L'ensemble des meubles s'appelle le", "words": [196, 197, 198, 199, 200]}, {"id": 38, "text": "10.", "words": [201]}, {"id": 39, "text": "Je lave les légumes dans l’", "words": [202, 203, 204, 205, 206, 207]}, {"id": 40, "text": "ED Vrai ou faux ?", "words": [208, 209, 210, 211, 212]}, {"id": 41, "text": "D 1 —", "words": [213, 214, 215]}, {"id": 42, "text": "Tests 122 à 125", "words": [216, 217, 218, 219]}, {"id": 43, "text": ".", "words": [220]}, {"id": 44, "text": "Nous mettons la voiture dans le grenier.", "words": [221, 222, 223, 224, 225, 226, 227]}, {"id": 45, "text": ".", "words": [228]}, {"id": 46, "text": "On peut manger dans la cuisine.", "words": [229, 230, 231, 232, 233, 234]}, {"id": 47, "text": ".", "words": [235]}, {"id": 48, "text": "confortablement installé sur le canapé.", "words": [236, 237, 238, 239, 240]}, {"id": 49, "text": ".", "words": [241]}, {"id": 50, "text": "range les bouteilles de vin dans la cave.", "words": [242, 243, 244